reviews.review_text: The grapes are all brown on the bottom of entire bag!! There are even some brown grapes throughout the entire bag!! I tried an all green grape and it was completely mush!! I'd like to give this bag of grapes back to you and get a NEW, FRESH BAG OF GREEN GRAPES, please.

These grapes are advertised for $5.33, I received a bag of grapes so small that it was $2.88. I understand they are weight adjusted but I'm very disappointed. When I tell you there are barely any grapes I mean it. It seems like this bag just got all the extra single grapes laying around.

My bag of grapes was delivered to me open with over half the grapes clearly missing from the bag. I am positive my driver was eating my grapes as she was delivering my order to me. I have had these brand of grapes before and never have they been like this. Someone should be fired
